dc:description: Light buff micaceous clay.  Semi-circular nozzle extends across rim, small stamped circle on either side of base.  Plain rim, scroll-shaped projection with two stamped dots at base at either side of lamp.  Two circular raised bands set off by grooves between rim and discus.  Four-leaved rosette in relief on discus, with central filling hole as center.  Ring handle, two grooves on upper half.  Base ring set off by grooves.  Two small concentric circles stamped in center of reverse.
